    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《梦闪少女》</strong>是一款双角色 roguelite 动作游戏，融合了科幻与奇幻元素。你将化身为被选中的高中女孩，为了拯救被困的梦囚，驾驶梦游机甲不断潜入梦境世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这不仅是一个少女们拯救世界的故事，也是一个少女同心协力、彼此救赎的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>※ 本作支持单人与双人游玩。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253950/extras/11bad7e8936922e0eb4aede2324c40bd.avif?t=1769643209\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253950/extras_big/11bad7e8936922e0eb4aede2324c40bd.avif?t=1769643209 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253950/extras/1e4de46789ddd21efe192810c79015c0.poster.avif?t=1769643209\" width=592 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253950/extras/1e4de46789ddd21efe192810c79015c0.webm?t=1769643209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253950/extras/1e4de46789ddd21efe192810c79015c0.mp4?t=1769643209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆ 多元流派战斗体验 ◆</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>要近战破坏？还是远距压制？由你决定！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从 4 名角色中选择 2 名出战，搭配关卡中随机掉落的 Roguelite 芯片，打造独一无二的战斗流派。同一把武器在不同角色手中，将激发出截然不同的火花！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 双人合作：在实验室自由调整最强搭档组合。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 单人游玩：电脑队友神助攻，还可随时切换主控角色，打出华丽连段！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关键词：芯片构筑、Roguelite、清版动作</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253950/extras/11bad7e8936922e0eb4aede2324c40bd.avif?t=1769643209\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253950/extras_big/11bad7e8936922e0eb4aede2324c40bd.avif?t=1769643209 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253950/extras/f0503f277cb06a8ef0fd5f335cdb6ddb.poster.avif?t=1769643209\" width=650 height=366 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253950/extras/f0503f277cb06a8ef0fd5f335cdb6ddb.webm?t=1769643209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253950/extras/f0503f277cb06a8ef0fd5f335cdb6ddb.mp4?t=1769643209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆ 梦闪涡轮 x 合体变身 ◆</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >梦闪涡轮会将噩梦体能量转化为爆发性战力，速度更快，火力更猛！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战况危急时，你拥有多样化的战术选择：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 梦闪组装：把伙伴装到身上，化身移动炮塔，提供极致火力掩护！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 合体变身：两人同步共鸣，融合为终极机甲形态，以无敌之姿粉碎全场噩梦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关键词：合作、双角色、机甲合体</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253950/extras/11bad7e8936922e0eb4aede2324c40bd.avif?t=1769643209\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253950/extras_big/11bad7e8936922e0eb4aede2324c40bd.avif?t=1769643209 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253950/extras/579b9a678253214aacd91af6e95bf38d.poster.avif?t=1769643209\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253950/extras/579b9a678253214aacd91af6e95bf38d.webm?t=1769643209\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253950/extras/579b9a678253214aacd91af6e95bf38d.mp4?t=1769643209\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>◆ 梦境与现实交织的故事 ◆</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>「我……能和大家成为朋友吗？」</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >梦境，是现实记忆的折射。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驾驶机甲的少女们潜入深层意识，面对的不仅是狰狞的噩梦体，更是人们心中扭曲的幻想与空洞。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这场救援行动中，你将逐步揭开梦境崩坏的真相......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关键词：叙事、少女</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253950/extras/11bad7e8936922e0eb4aede2324c40bd.avif?t=1769643209\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253950/extras_big/11bad7e8936922e0eb4aede2324c40bd.avif?t=1769643209 width=800 height=53 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >把《Awaking Beauty》加入愿望单，追踪 Demo 与 Playtest 更新。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>「我们需要您的反馈」</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们期待收到玩家们对于这款游戏的反馈。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎加入 Discord 让我们知道您们最喜欢它哪里、还有什么可以更好，许愿有机会被实现喔！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
